data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 3 bath home conveniently located near the I-10 for an easy commute. This well-maintained residence exudes a warm and inviting ambiance, offering a perfect blend of modern amenities and traditional charm. As you step through the front door, you are greeted by a spacious and light-filled living area, perfect for both relaxation and entertaining guests. The heart of this home lies in the well-appointed kitchen, featuring sleek quartz countertops, beautiful island, contemporary appliances, gas stove and ample storage space. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the kitchen to the dining area. Upstairs you will find 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and laundry room. Backyard is perfect for outdoor gatherings, featuring decorative gravel, pavers and turf. Don't miss out on this beautiful home!
